Package: dovecot-fetchmail
Architecture: any
Depends: ${shlibs:Depends}, ${misc:Depends}, dovecot-imapd (>= 1:2.0.0), fetchmail, ucf (>= 2.0020)
Description: Dovecot plugin that wakes up fetchmail
 dovecot-fetchmail provides a plugin for the Dovecot IMAP server that
 awakens a sleeping fetchmail daemon whenever an IMAP client calls
 the IMAP "IDLE, "NOOP" or "STATUS" commands.
